{"tid":727361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"dllm 我前世係咪同蜜蜂有仇","createTime":"2018-07-03T03:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T08:38:15.000Z","uid":155361,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"56aecb361ac949e03ede5707ccaae25d766626e7","tid":727361,"uid":155361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的 岩岩我係床到訓緊教時  無啦啦醒左覺得好似有條頭髮咁痴住隻腳飄下飄下咁 （因為我間房無開燈都幾黑  個時又無咩為意）咁我想踢走佢啦  我係咁咦踢兩腳啦 咁我feel到好似甩左  我放返隻腳落床  屌一放我隻腳痛左下 又有啲痹住咁（仆街啦我feel到係似曾相識既感覺） 跟住用床邊電話開電筒 一照 dllm又係🐝 佢仲係牆上邊 爬下爬下（好似無咩力 因為蜜蜂針完 好似會就瓜）<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/111852_7b13a29790ed317c3bf151f3c5eb3a70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F111852_7b13a29790ed317c3bf151f3c5eb3a70.png&h=a8a133d7&s={SIZE}\" /> 我即刻落床睇下支針係唔係隻腳到 觀察左陣應該無咩事<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲又係成撚日比蜜蜂搞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：計埋今次好似係屋企已經比蜜蜂針過4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0076122335f124571a60b628d98275c5505b2e0","tid":727361,"uid":70538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"唔似蜜蜂wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b6f58a42913dfb788973fc6b80d6928d576581","tid":727361,"uid":155361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0076122335f124571a60b628d98275c5505b2e0","tid":727361,"uid":70538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"唔似蜜蜂wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"打錯左好似係土蜂"},{"pid":"1af5c8fd10f710f11dcf3a112c6feec928d5ac77","tid":727361,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:29:45.000Z","msg":"樓主有咩遺言"},{"pid":"b33ad8c00ad12b1a6